Package fi.luupanu.skrapple.domain

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Board
    Board is the main board used by the game.
    Coord
    Each letter to be placed on the Board has a Coord(inate), a (x,y) destination.
    Dictionary
    The Dictionary class houses the word list used to evaluate if a word will be approved or not.
    Game
    Game stores and returns all the classes required for a SkrappleGame.
    Letter
    The Letter class is a representation of letter tiles in Skrapple.
    LetterBag
    LetterBag stores 101 Letters as per the rules of the game.
    Player
    The main Player class.
    Rack
    Every player has a unique rack that stores up to 7 letters.
    Square
    Board is comprised of 225 Squares.
    WildLetter
    Wild letters are letters that any letter type can be assigned to but they always score 0 points.
    Word
    Words are made of letters.
